overview.en: OZC (short for Ozcoin) is a chip issued in the Oz ecosystem. Anchored to BUSD, OZC can be used for various services including betting and gambling on Ozbet, as well as purchasing in Oz shopping applications.
overview.zh: OZC即Ozcoin，是一种发行于Oz生态的筹码，与稳定币BUSD锚定，可以用于Ozbet投注娱乐或生态内的各种服务购买和应用消费，持有Ozcoin是提升Oz生态会员等级并享受多种优惠的必要条件。
